        Subject-Predicate Phrases
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16971' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǔ wèi cízǔ', 'a subject-predicate phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主谓词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2750' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ànzhào', 'according to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">按照</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=14279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chénshù', 'to declare / to state')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">陈述</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=426' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bèi', 'by')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">被</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=14279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chénshù', 'to declare / to state')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">陈述</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=262' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'guānxì', 'relations')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">关系</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4639' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zǔhé', 'to assemble / to combine')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">组合</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1643' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qǐlai', 'beginning or continuing an action / stand up / get out of bed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">起来</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        A subject-predicate phrase combines the constituents in a subject-predicate relation.
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4167' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tóufa', 'hair on the head')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">头发</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2840' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duǎn', 'short / lacking')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">短</a>
          [hair is short]
          （“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4167' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tóufa', 'hair on the head')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">头发</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2681' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǔ', 'owner / host')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主</a>，“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2840' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duǎn', 'short / lacking')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">短</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4267' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'to speak of')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓</a>）
          （<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4167' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tóufa', 'hair on the head')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">头发</a> is the subject <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2840' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duǎn', 'short / lacking')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">短</a> is the predicate）
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4283' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiě', 'to write')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">写</a>
          [he writes]
          （“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2681' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǔ', 'owner / host')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主</a>，“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4283' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiě', 'to write')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">写</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4267' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'to speak of')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓</a>）
          （<a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他</a>”is the subject，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4283' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiě', 'to write')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">写</a> is the predicate）
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2681' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǔ', 'owner / host')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4267' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'to speak of')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9257' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cízǔ', 'phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=332' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhōng', 'middle / during')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">中</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qiánbian', 'front')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">前边</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2681' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǔ', 'owner / host')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主</a>”，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9344' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hòubiān', 'back')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">后边</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4267' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'to speak of')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓</a>”。“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2681' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǔ', 'owner / host')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=426' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bèi', 'by')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">被</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=14279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chénshù', 'to declare / to state')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">陈述</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4614' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duìxiàng', 'partner / boyfriend / girlfriend')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">对象</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1641' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jīngcháng', 'frequently / constantly / regularly / often')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">经常</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9288' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'míngcí', 'noun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">名词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9292' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dàicí', 'pronoun')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">代词</a>。“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4267' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'to speak of')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=14279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chénshù', 'to declare / to state')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">陈述</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2681' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǔ', 'owner / host')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1641' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jīngcháng', 'frequently / constantly / regularly / often')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">经常</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xíngróngcí', 'adjective')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">形容词</a>。“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2681' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǔ', 'owner / host')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4267' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'to speak of')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=312' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liǎng', 'two')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">两</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5495' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cí', 'word / works / phrases / classical Chinese poem / diction')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=389' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhījiān', 'between / among')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">之间</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10184' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'búyòng', 'need not')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">不用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2056' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rènhé', 'any / whatever / whichever')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">任何</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9265' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xūcí', 'function words / words having a grammatical function only')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">虚词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2461' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liánjiē', 'to link / to join / to attach')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">连接</a>。
      </p>
      <p>
        In a subject-predicate sentence the subject is first and the predicate is second.
        The subject is the object of the statement and is often a noun or pronoun.
        The predicate makes a statement about the subject and is usually a verb or adjective.
        No function words are used between the subject and predicate.
      </p>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='verb_object_phrases'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16972' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòng bīn cízǔ', 'a verb-object phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动宾词组</a>
        Verb-Object Phrases
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16972' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòng bīn cízǔ', 'a verb-object phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动宾词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2750' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ànzhào', 'according to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">按照</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=949' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhīpèi', 'to arrange / to allocate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">支配</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=426' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bèi', 'by')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">被</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=949' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhīpèi', 'to arrange / to allocate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">支配</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=262' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'guānxì', 'relations')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">关系</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4639' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zǔhé', 'to assemble / to combine')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">组合</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1643' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qǐlai', 'beginning or continuing an action / stand up / get out of bed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">起来</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        In a verb-object phrase the constituents are arranged in a verb-object relation.
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4882' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hē', 'to drink')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">喝</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1609' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shuǐ', 'water / river')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">水</a>
          [to drink water] 
