        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">行为</a>。
      </p>
      <p>
        The verb always comes first.  The order in a verb-object phrase is fixed.
        The first word is a transitive verb, expressing an action or behavior.
      </p>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='coordinative_phrases'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16970' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liánhé cízǔ', 'a coordinative phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">联合词组</a>
        Coordinative Phrases
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16970' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liánhé cízǔ', 'a coordinative phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">联合词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=951' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yóu', 'follow / from / it is for...to / reason / cause')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">由</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=312' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liǎng', 'two')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">两</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huòzhě', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或者</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=312' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liǎng', 'two')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">两</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=365' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǐshàng', 'more than / above / over / the above-mentioned')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">以上</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16188' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tónglèi', 'a person or object of the same kind')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">同类</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9257' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cízǔ', 'phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1540' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'to join')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">合</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1643' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qǐlai', 'beginning or continuing an action / stand up / get out of bed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">起来</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9195' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bìngliè', 'to stand side by side / to be juxtaposed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">并列</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=262' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'guānxì', 'relations')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">关系</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        A coordinative phrase is formed by two or more words or phrases of the same type to express
        a coordinative relation. For example, 
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a> [You and me] （“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a>”、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=757' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dōu', 'all')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">都</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9292' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dàicí', 'pronoun')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">代词</a>） （“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a>”、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a>” are both pronouns）
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9460' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiǎoxīn', 'to be careful')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">小心</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=803' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dì', 'earth / ground / place')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">地</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1205' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rènzhēn', 'earnest / serious')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">认真</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=803' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dì', 'earth / ground / place')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">地</a> [careful and serious] （“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9460' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiǎoxīn', 'to be careful')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">小心</a>”、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1205' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rènzhēn', 'earnest / serious')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">认真</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=757' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dōu', 'all')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">都</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xíngróngcí', 'adjective')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">形容词</a>）（“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9460' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiǎoxīn', 'to be careful')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">小心</a>”、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1205' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rènzhēn', 'earnest / serious')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">认真</a>” are both adjectives）
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16970' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liánhé cízǔ', 'a coordinative phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">联合词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=332' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhōng', 'middle / during')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">中</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5495' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cí', 'word / works / phrases / classical Chinese poem / diction')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=389' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhījiān', 'between / among')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">之间</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9274' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liáncí', 'conjunction')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">连词</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16957' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dùnhào', 'slight pause mark / serial comma (、)')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">顿号</a>“、”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5495' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cí', 'word / works / phrases / classical Chinese poem / diction')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5495' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cí', 'word / works / phrases / classical Chinese poem / diction')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=389' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhījiān', 'between / among')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">之间</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1374' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liánhé', 'to combine / to join / to unite')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">联合</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=262' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'guānxì', 'relations')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">关系</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=312' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liǎng', 'two')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">两</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=365' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǐshàng', 'more than / above / over / the above-mentioned')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">以上</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5495' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cí', 'word / works / phrases / classical Chinese poem / diction')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1374' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liánhé', 'to combine / to join / to unite')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">联合</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=524' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shí', 'time / at that time')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">时</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9274' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liáncí', 'conjunction')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">连词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10452' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zuìhòu', 'final / last')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">最后</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5495' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cí', 'word / works / phrases / classical Chinese poem / diction')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qiánbian', 'front')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">前边</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>:
      </p>
      <p>
        The terms in a coordinative phrase may be separated by conjunction.
        The serial comma “、” can also be used to separate words in in a coordinative phrase.
        When more than two words are joined, a conjunction is placed before the last one.
        For example,
      </p>
      <pre>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4023' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēge', 'elder brother')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">哥哥</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4989' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiějie', 'older sister')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">姐姐</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=757' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dōu', 'all')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">都</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=584' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shàng', 'above / previous')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">上</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dàxué', 'university / college')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">大学</a>。(My older brother, older sister, and I all go to university.)
      </pre>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16970' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liánhé cízǔ', 'a coordinative phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">联合词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=951' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yóu', 'follow / from / it is for...to / reason / cause')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">由</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǎ', 'which / who / what')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">哪</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4536' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lèi', 'kind / type / class / category')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">类</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5495' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cí', 'word / works / phrases / classical Chinese poem / diction')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1993' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gòuchéng', 'to constitute / to form / to compose')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">构成</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=902' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiù', 'right away / only')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">就</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1746' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jùyǒu', 'to have / to possess')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">具有</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǎ', 'which / who / what')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">哪</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4536' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lèi', 'kind / type / class / category')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">类</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5495' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cí', 'word / works / phrases / classical Chinese poem / diction')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=8533' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòngtú', 'use / application')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用途</a>。
      </p>
      <p>
        A coordinative phrase has the same uses as the constituent parts that it is made from.
      </p>
