      <p>
        In an endocentric phrase the constituents are combined such that the first one decorates or
        limits the second.
        Endocentric phrases can be divided into two kinds: nominal endocentric phrases and 
        endocentric phrase where the second constituent is either a verb or an adjective.
        In a nominal endocentric phrase the second part is a noun.
        For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=13104' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rèdài', 'the tropics')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">热带</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4181' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'sēnlín', 'forest / woods')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">森林</a>.
        In this sentence, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=13104' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'rèdài', 'the tropics')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">热带</a> is the first part and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4181' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'sēnlín', 'forest / woods')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">森林</a>, the second part is a noun.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1347' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xìng', 'sex / nature / surname / suffix corresponding to -ness')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">性</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xíngróngcí', 'adjective')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">形容词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1347' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xìng', 'sex / nature / surname / suffix corresponding to -ness')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">性</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piān zhèng cízǔ', 'an endocentric phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">偏正词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=925' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yě', 'also')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">也</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4616' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiù shì', 'is precisely / is exactly')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">就是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1149' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hòu', 'after / later / behind')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">后</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2190' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bùfèn', 'part / share / section / piece')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">部分</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=372' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'for / to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">为</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xíngróngcí', 'adjective')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">形容词</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=376' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiángxì', 'detailed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">详细</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6251' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tǎolùn', 'to discuss / to talk over')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">讨论</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9257' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cízǔ', 'phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=332' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhōng', 'middle / during')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">中</a>，“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=376' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiángxì', 'detailed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">详细</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2878' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piān', 'to be one-sided / to lean / to slant / to be prejudiced / to be inclined')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">偏</a>”，“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6251' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tǎolùn', 'to discuss / to talk over')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">讨论</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=914' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhèng', 'main / upright / straight')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">正</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=925' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yě', 'also')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">也</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòngcí', 'verb')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=654' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hěn', 'very')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">很</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4924' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piàoliang', 'pretty / beautiful / elegant / polished')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">漂亮</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9257' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cízǔ', 'phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=332' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhōng', 'middle / during')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">中</a>，“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4924' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piàoliang', 'pretty / beautiful / elegant / polished')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">漂亮</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xíngróngcí', 'adjective')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">形容词</a>。
      </p>
      <p>
        In a verbal or adjectival endocentric phrase the second part is either a verb or an adjective.
        For example, in the phrase <a href='/word_detail.php?id=376' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiángxì', 'detailed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">详细</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6251' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tǎolùn', 'to discuss / to talk over')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">讨论</a>， <a href='/word_detail.php?id=6251' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tǎolùn', 'to discuss / to talk over')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">讨论</a> [to discuss in detail], the latter part is a verb.
        In the phrase <a href='/word_detail.php?id=654' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hěn', 'very')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">很</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4924' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piàoliang', 'pretty / beautiful / elegant / polished')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">漂亮</a> (very beautiful) the word <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4924' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piàoliang', 'pretty / beautiful / elegant / polished')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">漂亮</a> 
        [beautiful] is an adjective.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=3547' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒushí', 'sometimes')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有时</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'piān zhèng cízǔ', 'an endocentric phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">偏正词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=335' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yào', 'to want ')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">要</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9265' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xūcí', 'function words / words having a grammatical function only')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">虚词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2461' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liánjiē', 'to link / to join / to attach')" 
