        Numeral-Measure Word Phrases
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16974' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shùliàng cízǔ', 'a numeral-measure phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">数量词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=951' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yóu', 'follow / from / it is for...to / reason / cause')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">由</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9291' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shùcí', 'numeral')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">数词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9278' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liàngcí', 'measure word')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">量词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4639' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zǔhé', 'to assemble / to combine')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">组合</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1336' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ér', 'and / as well as / but (not) / yet (not)')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">而</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1932' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chéng', 'to finish / to complete / to accomplish / to succeed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">成</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1869' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zǔ', 'a group')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5495' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cí', 'word / works / phrases / classical Chinese poem / diction')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4536' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lèi', 'kind / type / class / category')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">类</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16974' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shùliàng cízǔ', 'a numeral-measure phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">数量词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=951' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yóu', 'follow / from / it is for...to / reason / cause')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">由</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9291' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shùcí', 'numeral')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">数词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9299' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'míngliàngcí', 'nominal measure word')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">名量词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1993' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gòuchéng', 'to constitute / to form / to compose')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">构成</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        A numeral-measure word phrase combines a numeral and a measure word into a phrase.
        One kind of numeral-measure word phrase combines a numeral and a nominal measure word.
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=923' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'běn', 'measure word for books')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">本</a> (one book)
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=312' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liǎng', 'two')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">两</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gè', 'individual / unit')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a> (two units)
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'sān', 'three')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">三</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9533' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liàng', 'measure word for vehicles')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">辆</a> (three vehicles)
        </li>
