          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他</a><span class='hl'>在北大</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1725' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xuéxí', 'to learn / to study')" 
