      <h4 class='article'>
        <a name='common_prepositional_phrases'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9803' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chángjiàn', 'common')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">常见</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=17004' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiècí jiégòu', 'prepositional phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">介词结构</a>
        Common Prepositional Patterns
      </h4>
      <p>
        “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a>…<a href='/word_detail.php?id=584' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shàng', 'above / previous')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">上</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1860' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòngzuò', 'movement / motion / action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动作</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1612' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jìnxíng', 'to advance / to conduct / to carry out')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">进行</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6241' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhuàngtài', 'status / state of affairs / state / mode')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">状态</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1291' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cúnzài', 'to exist')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">存在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1913' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chǎngsuǒ', 'location / place')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">场所</a>。“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a>…<a href='/word_detail.php?id=584' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shàng', 'above / previous')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">上</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=925' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yě', 'also')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">也</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3340' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fànwéi', 'range / scope / limit / extent')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">范围</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=725' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fāngmiàn', 'aspect / respect')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">方面</a>，“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=584' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shàng', 'above / previous')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">上</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=389' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhījiān', 'between / among')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">之间</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=400' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'indicates a number greater than the number preceding it')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">多</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=372' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'for / to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">为</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9332' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chōuxiàng', 'abstract')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">抽象</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9288' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'míngcí', 'noun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">名词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòngcí', 'verb')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        The form <a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a>…<a href='/word_detail.php?id=584' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shàng', 'above / previous')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">上</a> can express the place where an action takes place or a condition exists.
        The form <a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a>…<a href='/word_detail.php?id=584' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shàng', 'above / previous')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">上</a> can also be used to indicate scope or aspect when an
        abstract noun or verb is used in between.  For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=271' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhè', 'this / these')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">这</a><span class='hl'>在</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1145' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìshǐ', 'history')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">历史</a><span class='hl'>上</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10511' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bùshǎo', 'not just a few')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">不少</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>。
          [This is not uncommon throughout history.]
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他</a><span class='hl'>在</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=567' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huì', 'can / be possible / be able to / to assemble / to meet')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">会</a><span class='hl'>上</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1808' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xuānbù', 'to declare / to announce')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">宣布</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>。
          [He announced it in the meeting.]
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a>…<a href='/word_detail.php?id=580' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xià', 'next')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">下</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2730' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jùtǐ', 'concrete / definite / specific')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">具体</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1913' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chǎngsuǒ', 'location / place')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">场所</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huòzhě', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或者</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1714' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tiáojiàn', 'condition / prerequisite')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">条件</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=499' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qíngkuàng', 'circumstances / state of affairs / situation')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">情况</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        The form <a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a>…<a href='/word_detail.php?id=580' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xià', 'next')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">下</a> can indicate a concrete position or it can indicate a
        condition or situation.  For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <span class='hl'>在</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5009' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lǎoshī', 'teacher')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">老师</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1158' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bāngzhù', 'help / assistance / aid')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">帮助</a><span class='hl'>下</span>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=366' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒmen', 'we')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我们</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=757' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dōu', 'all')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">都</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=654' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hěn', 'very')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">很</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1114' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dà', 'big / huge / large / major')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">大</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5000' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jìnbù', 'progress')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">进步</a>。
          [With the help of our teachers we have all made great progress.]
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class='hl'>在</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=15080' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiāzhǎng', 'parents / the head of the family')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">家长</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3126' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gǔlì', 'to encourage')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">鼓励</a><span class='hl'>下</span>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=521' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tāmen', 'they')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他们</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4031' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'háizǐ', 'child')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">孩子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5634' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ná', 'to hold / to seize / to catch / to apprehend / to take')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">拿</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=603' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dào', 'arrive / receive')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">到</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=8169' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhège', 'this / this one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">这个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5651' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jīhuì', 'opportunity / chance / occasion')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">机会</a>。
          [With the encouragement of his parents, their child was able to obtain this opportunity.]
