      </ol>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='de_phrases'></a>
        “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=894' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zì', 'letter / symbol / character')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">字</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1620' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiégòu', 'structure / composition')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">结构</a>        
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a> Phrases
      </h3>
      <p>
        “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=894' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zì', 'letter / symbol / character')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">字</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1620' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiégòu', 'structure / composition')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">结构</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=951' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yóu', 'follow / from / it is for...to / reason / cause')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">由</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9306' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiégòu zhùcí', 'structural particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">结构助词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1943' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fù', 'to add / to attach / to be close to / to be attached')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">附</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9252' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shící', 'notional words / content words')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">实词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huòzhě', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或者</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9257' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cízǔ', 'phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词组</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9338' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hòumian', 'rear / back / behind / later / afterwards')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">后面</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4639' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zǔhé', 'to assemble / to combine')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">组合</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1336' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ér', 'and / as well as / but (not) / yet (not)')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">而</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1932' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chéng', 'to finish / to complete / to accomplish / to succeed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">成</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9257' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cízǔ', 'phrase')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词组</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        A <a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a> phrase is one where the structural particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a> is attached to a notional word or phrase.
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=271' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhè', 'this / these')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">这</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4909' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fèn', 'copy / part / share / portion')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">份</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2142' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bàozhǐ', 'newspaper')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">报纸</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><span class='hl'>人家的</span>。
          [This newspaper belongs to someone else.]
          （“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9292' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dàicí', 'pronoun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">代词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9338' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hòumian', 'rear / back / behind / later / afterwards')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">后面</a>）
          （<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a> is attached to a pronoun）
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=271' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhè', 'this / these')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">这</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3023' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhāng', 'sheet')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">张</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4736' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chuáng', 'bed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">床</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><span class='hl'>弟弟的</span>。
          [This bed is my younger brother's.]
          （“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9288' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'míngcí', 'noun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">名词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9338' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hòumian', 'rear / back / behind / later / afterwards')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">后面</a>）
          （<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a> is attached to a noun）
